-- MOVES-Stuart Cummins joins C. Hoare & Co as head of wealth management strategy
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bangalore
-- Wed Oct 01, 2014 06:14AM EDT
-- None



Oct 1 (Reuters) - UK-based private bank C. Hoare & Co said it appointed Stuart Cummins as head of wealth management strategy.

Cummins will work with Annamaria Koerling, head of wealth management, for the development and implementation of the overall strategy for the division as well as leading the bank's wealth planning team.